 The below example shows how to set the IsReadOnly in 
#[XAML](#tab/tabid-1)

<inputs:SfMaskedEntry
      x:Name="maskedEntry"
      IsReadOnly="true"
      HeightRequest="50"
      WidthRequest="200"/>

#[C#](#tab/tabid-2)

